---
import Icon from './Icon.astro';
---

<section class="box skills">
	<div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
		<Icon icon="code" color="var(--java-orange)" size="2.5rem" gradient />
		<h2>Informatics Engineer | Senior Full-Stack Java Specialist</h2>
		<div class="expertise-content">
			<p class="lead">Enterprise-grade solutions with:</p>
			<ul class="tech-highlights">
				<li>
					<strong>Vaadin 24</strong> - 28+ production deployments handling 50K+ daily users
					<span class="tech-tag">Type-Safe UIs</span>
				</li>
				<li>
					<strong>Spring Boot 3</strong> - Microservices with 99.98% uptime SLA
					<span class="tech-tag">Cloud Native</span>
				</li>
				<li>
					<strong>AI Integration</strong> - NLP-powered document processing (70% efficiency gain)
					<span class="tech-tag">OpenAI API</span>
				</li>
			</ul>
			<div class="metrics">
				<div class="metric">
					<span class="number">10+</span>
					<span class="label">Years Experience</span>
				</div>
				<div class="metric">
					<span class="number">40K+</span>
					<span class="label">Daily Users</span>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
		<Icon icon="languages" color="var(--accent-regular)" size="2.5rem" gradient />
		<h2>Multilingual Language Specialist</h2>
		<p>With proficiency in 5 languages, I bridge communication gaps and ensure clear, culturally aware interactions. My expertise in TESOL and TEFL allows me to engage in diverse global projects, delivering solutions that resonate across linguistic and cultural boundaries.</p>
	</div>
	<div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
		<Icon icon="strategy" color="var(--accent-regular)" size="2.5rem" gradient />
		<h2>Strategy-Minded</h2>
		<p>Combining my technical skills with strategic thinking, I approach projects with an innovative mindset. I leverage my Informatics Engineering background to design solutions that are both effective and forward-thinking, while ensuring clear communication in every step of the process.</p>
	</div>
</section>



<style>
	.box {
		border: 1px solid var(--gray-800);
		border-radius: 0.75rem;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		background-color: var(--gray-999_40);
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
	}

	.skills {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 3rem;
	}

	.skills h2 {
		font-size: var(--text-lg);
	}

	.skills p {
		color: var(--gray-400);
	}

	@media (min-width: 50em) {
		.box {
			border-radius: 1.5rem;
			padding: 2.5rem;
		}

		.skills {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
			gap: 5rem;
		}

		.skills h2 {
			font-size: var(--text-2xl);
		}
	}
</style>
